stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_default: value == trie.default
    [*] --> q_set: value != trie.default
    q_check_default --> q_check_exists: key in trie._data
    q_check_default --> q_done_noop: key not in trie._data
    q_check_exists --> q_delete: del trie._data[key]
    q_delete --> [*]
    q_done_noop --> [*]
    q_set --> q_assign: trie._data[key] = value
    q_assign --> [*]
